        "scene"
      ],
      "interactive": false,
      "description": "Marks this hook invocation as unhandled so the legacy input underneath it runs instead (e.g. map movement on up/down/left/right when no menu overlay is open). Any hook key otherwise intercepts its key unconditionally."
